  <text>
      <body>
         <div type="entry">
            <pb facs="https://leaf.bucknell.edu/sites/default/files/2026-01/diary81.jpg"/>
            <dateline>Thursday<date when="1862-06-26"/> 26</dateline>
            <p>A <name type="weather">pleasant day – air stirring</name>. We had Brigade drill but as I was officer of the
               day I did not go. I was busy too preparing <objectName type="readables">applications</objectName> for our officers for
               backpay. Been reading <persName>Mackenzie</persName>'s life of Dr Magin. He reminds me very much of
<persName> Dr Elder</persName> of <placeName cert="high" key="Philadelphia" ref="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BucknellDSC/jmlinn/refs/heads/main/jmlinn_gazetteer.xml#linnpl069">Philadelphia<precision match="@ref" precision="high"/></placeName> [torn] except the Dr is not near so learned. </p>
         </div>
      </body>
